{"tid":2348426,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"千年蟲騙案","createTime":"2020-12-31T16:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T23:52:28.000Z","uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5c7b16b253ed1343c9d85701c44b483c40b6bc47","tid":2348426,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:29:37.000Z","msg":"2000年前後，全球非常關注千年蟲問題，當中的「蟲」（bug）只是指電腦軟體由隱藏數值引起的失誤，只會影響電腦軟體的運作 ，對人體無害。但騙徒卻將其形容為一種真實的害蟲，誘騙對千年蟲問題一知半解的民眾購買，令他們以為千年蟲是一種類似瘟疫、傳染病等病毒，感染了的人類有可能死亡，藉此推銷「可殺死千年蟲」的殺蟲劑。很多時候，騙徒更會聲稱貨品可以高價轉手，能夠賺取豐厚的差價，吸引受害者大批購買。<br />\n<br />\n實例\t<br />\n一名婦人以為千年蟲是在肚子裏生長的蟲，被三名騙徒遊說買入一百粒價值三百元一粒的「千年蟲杜蟲藥」，連同現金、手鐲和戒指，被騙取了三萬多元。"},{"pid":"4c511ab35b4e2a43fc24f851aaf3bbf60ed83ec2","tid":2348426,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:30:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02528c564fb03102aa594fc87bd447d90d99967e","tid":2348426,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4c511ab35b4e2a43fc24f851aaf3bbf60ed83ec2","tid":2348426,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:30:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:34:45.000Z","msg":"你未出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbffb343820e99d9f2172e935a69cf5a886a7b9","tid":2348426,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"108dce8118b27e7428606d8b05452901bfdaa992","tid":2348426,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"新年快大雞樂"},{"pid":"66091a9287ad8d20b69164361fb3691580da6b2f","tid":2348426,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fbffb343820e99d9f2172e935a69cf5a886a7b9","tid":2348426,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"02528c564fb03102aa594fc87bd447d90d99967e","tid":2348426,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4c511ab35b4e2a43fc24f851aaf3bbf60ed83ec2"